		<item>
			<title>[포토] 내 마음의 풍경</title>
			<description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;img src="https://image.lawtimes.co.kr/thumb/180/203473.jpg" alt="0.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;저무는 가을의 숨결이 처마 끝 풍경을 살며시 흔들며 지나간다.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: right;"&gt;   &lt;b&gt;백성현 기자  stwhite@lawtimes.co.kr&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			<pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 20:07:01 -0000</pubDate>
			<category>news</category>
			<link>https://www.lawtimes.co.kr/news/203473</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.lawtimes.co.kr/news/203473</guid>
